  "title": "Clinic Staff Nurse (Up to $4200, Office hours, 5.5 days) #HCG",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities </strong></p><p><ul><li>Provide nursing care, assist doctors during consultations and procedures, and administer treatments.</li><li>Monitor patients, take vital signs, and carry out basic clinical procedures.</li><li>Educate patients on care instructions and support a positive clinic experience.</li><li>Maintain accurate records, manage supplies, and ensure infection control standards.</li><li>Work closely with the healthcare team to ensure smooth daily clinic operations.</li></ul></p><p><br /><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma/ Degree in Nursing </li><li>Valid SNB and BCLS </li><li>Min 1 year experience in nursing / healthcare industry </li><li>Training will be provided </li></ul><p><br />All qualified applicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p>triciagoh@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p></p>",
